<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Templates Library - Royal AI™</title>

  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
  <%= javascript_importmap_tags %>

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f0f 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
      color: #eee;
      min-height: 100vh;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .hero-section {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
      color: #ffd700;
    }

    .hero-icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-shadow: 0 0 30px #ffd700;
    }

    .hero-tagline {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      opacity: 0.9;
      color: #ccc;
    }

    .content-section {
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .search-filter {
      background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.85);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    }

    .search-input {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border: 2px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
      border-radius: 25px;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem auto;
      display: block;
    }

    .search-input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #ffd700;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .filter-tabs {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .filter-tab {
      background: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid #ffd700;
      border-radius: 25px;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      color: #ffd700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .filter-tab.active,
    .filter-tab:hover {
      background: #ffd700;
      color: #000;
    }

    .templates-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin: 3rem 0;
    }

    .template-card {
      background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.85);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 2rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      color: #ddd;
    }

    .template-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      border-color: #ffd700;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .template-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .template-emoji {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .template-info h3 {
      color: #ffd700;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .template-agent {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .template-description {
      color: #ccc;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .template-content {
      background: rgba(40, 40, 40, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid #555;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin: 1rem 0;
      font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', 'Consolas', monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      position: relative;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }

    .copy-button {
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      right: 10px;
      background: #ffd700;
      color: #000;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .copy-button:hover {
      background: #ffcc00;
    }

    .template-tags {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .template-tag {
      background: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
      color: #ffd700;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 15px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .use-template-btn {
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ffd700, #ffcc00);
      color: #000;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .use-template-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.4);
    }

    .section-title {
      color: #ffd700;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 3rem 0 2rem 0;
    }

    .category-section {
      margin: 3rem 0;
    }

    .category-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .category-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .category-title {
      color: #ffd700;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .tips-section {
      background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.85);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin: 3rem 0;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    }

    .tips-section h3 {
      color: #ffd700;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .tip-item {
      margin: 0.8rem 0;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      position: relative;
      color: #ccc;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .tip-item::before {
      content: "💡";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
    }

    /* Repository Showcase Styles */
    .repo-showcase {
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .showcase-intro {
      background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.85);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    }

    .github-main-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(40, 40, 60, 0.95) 0%, rgba(20, 20, 30, 0.95) 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .github-main-link:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(50, 50, 70, 0.95) 0%, rgba(30, 30, 50, 0.95) 100%);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
      border-color: #ffd700;
    }

    .github-icon {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .external-icon {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .repo-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .repo-card {
      background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.85);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 2rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      color: #ddd;
    }

    .repo-card.featured {
      border-color: #ffaa00;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(40, 40, 60, 0.95) 0%, rgba(20, 20, 30, 0.95) 100%);
    }

    .repo-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      border-color: #ffd700;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .repo-card.featured:hover {
      border-color: #ffaa00;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(255, 170, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .repo-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .repo-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .repo-info h4 {
      color: #ffd700;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .repo-path {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', 'Consolas', monospace;
    }

    .featured-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: -0.5rem;
      right: 0;
      background: #ffaa00;
      color: #000;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 15px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .repo-description {
      color: #ccc;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .repo-features {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .feature-tag {
      background: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.15);
      color: #ffd700;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .repo-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .repo-btn {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 120px;
      padding: 0.7rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }

    .repo-btn.primary {
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ffd700, #ffcc00);
      color: #000;
    }

    .repo-btn.primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.4);
    }

    .repo-btn.secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: #ffd700;
      border-color: #ffd700;
    }

    .repo-btn.secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .all-repos-section {
      background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.85);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      margin: 3rem 0;
      text-align: center;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    }

    .view-all-repos-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(40, 40, 60, 0.95) 0%, rgba(20, 20, 30, 0.95) 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .view-all-repos-btn:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(50, 50, 70, 0.95) 0%, rgba(30, 30, 50, 0.95) 100%);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
      border-color: #ffd700;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .templates-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      
      .template-card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }

      .repo-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .repo-actions {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .repo-btn {
        flex: none;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-icon">�</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Templates Library</h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Ready-to-use prompts and templates for all Royal AI™ agents</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <!-- Search and Filter -->
    <div class="search-filter">
      <input type="text" class="search-input" placeholder="🔍 Search templates..." id="template-search">
      <div class="filter-tabs">
        <div class="filter-tab active" data-category="all">All Templates</div>
        <div class="filter-tab" data-category="content">Content Creation</div>
        <div class="filter-tab" data-category="companion">AI Companions</div>
        <div class="filter-tab" data-category="development">Development</div>
        <div class="filter-tab" data-category="education">Education</div>
        <div class="filter-tab" data-category="business">Business</div>
        <div class="filter-tab" data-category="creative">Creative</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Creation Templates -->
    <div class="category-section" data-category="content">
      <div class="category-header">
        <span class="category-icon">✍️</span>
        <h2 class="category-title">Content Creation Templates</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="templates-grid">
        <div class="template-card" data-category="content">
          <div class="template-header">
            <span class="template-emoji">📝</span>
            <div class="template-info">
              <h3>Blog Post Outline</h3>
              <div class="template-agent">ContentCrafter</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="template-description">
            Create comprehensive blog post outlines with engaging hooks, structured content, and strong conclusions.
          </p>
          <div class="template-content">
            <button class="copy-button" onclick="copyTemplate(this)">Copy</button>
Create a detailed blog post outline for "[TOPIC]" targeting [TARGET_AUDIENCE].

Include:
- Compelling headline with SEO keywords
- Engaging introduction hook
- 5-7 main sections with subpoints
- Actionable takeaways
- Strong conclusion with CTA

Tone: [Professional/Casual/Friendly]
Length: [Short/Medium/Long] format
          </div>
          <div class="template-tags">
            <span class="template-tag">Blog Writing</span>
            <span class="template-tag">SEO</span>
            <span class="template-tag">Content Strategy</span>
          </div>
          <button class="use-template-btn">Use This Template</button>
        </div>

        <div class="template-card" data-category="content">
          <div class="template-header">
            <span class="template-emoji">📱</span>
            <div class="template-info">
              <h3>Social Media Campaign</h3>
              <div class="template-agent">ContentCrafter</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="template-description">
            Generate engaging social media content for various platforms with platform-specific optimization.
          </p>
          <div class="template-content">
            <button class="copy-button" onclick="copyTemplate(this)">Copy</button>
Create a 7-day social media campaign for [PRODUCT/SERVICE].

Platforms: [Instagram/Twitter/LinkedIn/TikTok]
Goal: [Brand awareness/Sales/Engagement]

For each day, provide:
- Platform-optimized caption
- Relevant hashtags (5-10)
- Visual content suggestions
- Best posting times
- Engagement strategies

Brand voice: [Describe brand personality]
          </div>
          <div class="template-tags">
            <span class="template-tag">Social Media</span>
            <span class="template-tag">Marketing</span>
            <span class="template-tag">Campaign</span>
          </div>
          <button class="use-template-btn">Use This Template</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- AI Companions Templates -->
    <div class="category-section" data-category="companion">
      <div class="category-header">
        <span class="category-icon">❤️</span>
        <h2 class="category-title">AI Companion Templates</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="templates-grid">
        <div class="template-card" data-category="companion">
          <div class="template-header">
            <span class="template-emoji">🤗</span>
            <div class="template-info">
              <h3>Emotional Support Session</h3>
              <div class="template-agent">EmotiSense</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="template-description">
            Get empathetic emotional support and guidance through difficult feelings or situations.
          </p>
          <div class="template-content">
            <button class="copy-button" onclick="copyTemplate(this)">Copy</button>
Hi EmotiSense, I'm feeling [EMOTION] about [SITUATION].

I need help with:
- Understanding these feelings
- Processing what happened
- Finding healthy coping strategies
- Building emotional resilience

Please be gentle and supportive in your response. I'm looking for compassion and practical guidance.

Current stress level: [1-10]
What would help most right now: [Listening/Advice/Distraction/Techniques]
          </div>
          <div class="template-tags">
            <span class="template-tag">Emotional Support</span>
            <span class="template-tag">Mental Health</span>
            <span class="template-tag">Coping</span>
          </div>
          <button class="use-template-btn">Use This Template</button>
        </div>

        <div class="template-card" data-category="companion">
          <div class="template-header">
            <span class="template-emoji">🧠</span>
            <div class="template-info">
              <h3>Memory Organization</h3>
              <div class="template-agent">Memora</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="template-description">
            Organize and structure important information for easy recall and knowledge building.
          </p>
          <div class="template-content">
            <button class="copy-button" onclick="copyTemplate(this)">Copy</button>
Help me organize and remember information about [TOPIC/SUBJECT].

Information to process:
[Paste your content, notes, or data here]

Please help me:
- Create a clear knowledge structure
- Identify key concepts and connections
- Build memory associations
- Suggest review schedules
- Create easy recall triggers

Learning style: [Visual/Auditory/Kinesthetic]
Priority level: [High/Medium/Low]
          </div>
          <div class="template-tags">
            <span class="template-tag">Memory</span>
            <span class="template-tag">Learning</span>
            <span class="template-tag">Organization</span>
          </div>
          <button class="use-template-btn">Use This Template</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Development Templates -->
    <div class="category-section" data-category="development">
      <div class="category-header">
        <span class="category-icon">⚡</span>
        <h2 class="category-title">Development Templates</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="templates-grid">
        <div class="template-card" data-category="development">
          <div class="template-header">
            <span class="template-emoji">🔧</span>
            <div class="template-info">
              <h3>Code Review & Optimization</h3>
              <div class="template-agent">CodeForge</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="template-description">
            Get comprehensive code review with optimization suggestions and best practices.
          </p>
          <div class="template-content">
            <button class="copy-button" onclick="copyTemplate(this)">Copy</button>
Please review and optimize this [LANGUAGE] code:

```[LANGUAGE]
[Paste your code here]
```

Focus on:
- Performance optimization
- Code readability
- Security vulnerabilities
- Best practices compliance
- Error handling
- Documentation improvements

Project context: [Brief description]
Performance requirements: [Specific needs]
Target audience: [Beginners/Intermediate/Advanced]
          </div>
          <div class="template-tags">
            <span class="template-tag">Code Review</span>
            <span class="template-tag">Optimization</span>
            <span class="template-tag">Best Practices</span>
          </div>
          <button class="use-template-btn">Use This Template</button>
        </div>

        <div class="template-card" data-category="development">
          <div class="template-header">
            <span class="template-emoji">🌐</span>
            <div class="template-info">
              <h3>Research & Analysis</h3>
              <div class="template-agent">NetScope</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="template-description">
            Conduct comprehensive research and data analysis for projects and decision-making.
          </p>
          <div class="template-content">
            <button class="copy-button" onclick="copyTemplate(this)">Copy</button>
Research and analyze: [RESEARCH TOPIC]

Scope:
- Market trends and statistics
- Competitor analysis
- Technology landscape
- User preferences and behavior
- Industry best practices

Deliverables needed:
- Summary of key findings
- Data visualization suggestions
- Actionable recommendations
- Risk assessment
- Implementation timeline

Target market: [Define audience]
Budget considerations: [If applicable]
          </div>
          <div class="template-tags">
            <span class="template-tag">Research</span>
            <span class="template-tag">Analysis</span>
            <span class="template-tag">Market Intelligence</span>
          </div>
          <button class="use-template-btn">Use This Template</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Education Templates -->
    <div class="category-section" data-category="education">
      <div class="category-header">
        <span class="category-icon">🎓</span>
        <h2 class="category-title">Educational Templates</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="templates-grid">
        <div class="template-card" data-category="education">
          <div class="template-header">
            <span class="template-emoji">👨‍🏫</span>
            <div class="template-info">
              <h3>Kid-Friendly Learning</h3>
              <div class="template-agent">KiddieAI Tutor</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="template-description">
            Age-appropriate learning sessions that make complex topics fun and engaging for children.
          </p>
          <div class="template-content">
            <button class="copy-button" onclick="copyTemplate(this)">Copy</button>
Hi KiddieAI! I'm [AGE] years old and want to learn about [TOPIC].

Please teach me:
- What is [TOPIC]?
- Why is it important?
- Fun facts I should know
- Simple examples I can understand
- Activities or games to practice

Make it:
- Age-appropriate for [AGE]
- Fun and engaging
- Easy to understand
- Interactive when possible

My favorite subjects: [List interests]
Learning style: [How child learns best]
          </div>
          <div class="template-tags">
            <span class="template-tag">Kids Learning</span>
            <span class="template-tag">Interactive</span>
            <span class="template-tag">Age-Appropriate</span>
          </div>
          <button class="use-template-btn">Use This Template</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Creative Templates -->
    <div class="category-section" data-category="creative">
      <div class="category-header">
